info.desc: This is the door from Nolte Center Garage to Folwell Hall.
info.instr: Go to Nolte Center Garage. Make your way towards the west-most point.

info.desc: This is the door from Nolte Center Garage to 10 Church st.
info.instr: There should be a door that leads to a short hall with stairs, go right.
Straight ahead is a door that leads into Folwell Hall, take a right at it.
On the left after walking to the next wall of the garage is an entrance to 10 Church St
